👉 Constructor vs Method

| Feature     | Constructor       | Method                |
| ----------- | ----------------- | --------------------- |
| Name        | Same as class     | Any name              |
| Return Type | No return type    | Must have return type |
| Call        | Automatic         | Manual                |
| Purpose     | Initialize object | Perform operations    |

